title: MS-DOS 5.0 Floppy Disks 1, 2 and 3
description:
*************************************************************************************

                              MS-DOS 5.0 Floppy Disks
*************************************************************************************

I bring You MS-DOS 5.0, The better MS-DOS OS!!! (hehe) 

How To Install:

Start Microsoft Virtual PC, (or virtualbox)
Insert Floppy Disk 1
OK, follow the on screen instructions
When prompted, insert disk 2
Follow the on screen inscructions
When Prompted, Insert disk 3
Follow the on screen inscructions
Restart the computer (virtual machine)
Make sure there is no floppy images in the virtual machine
It has finshed!!!


Hope you enjoy!! :)
